Verdict? The best vaccine is the one available! CanSino and Sputnik-V both secure you from severe disease. 

Vaccine doesn't ensure you will never get Covid-19. All it does is ensure if you do get it the immune system will kick in and save you quicker!

Get the shot(s).

The Sputnik-V uses two different adenoviruses: Ad5 and Ad26. The advantage is human population hasn't developed large scale immunity to Ad26 thus it makes body work harder and thus perfects immunity against covid.

Thus it's efficacy is high.

Further simple, think of adenoviruse vaccine as a ballon. It is then filled with small part of Sars-Cov-2 (Covid-19) and injected into your body. Your body already knows how to destroy adenovirus and in doing so it destroys spike protein of covid & remembers. Trojan horse.
